     But[0m[2m `[0m[2mdecrement[0m[2m`[0m[2m has[0m[2m a guard[0m[2m check too[0m[2m. The[0m[2m issue though[0m[2m is[0m[2m the[0m[2m **[0m[2mTime[0m[2m-of[0m[2m-check[0m[2m to time[0m[2m-of-use[0m[2m (TO[0m[2mCT[0m[2mOU)**[0m[2m race condition[0m[2m:[0m[2m
