     The[0m[2m core problem[0m[2m is a[0m[2m race[0m[2m condition:[0m[2m orders[0m[2m check[0m[2m stock availability[0m[2m, but[0m[2m by[0m[2m the time[0m[2m they attempt[0m[2m to decrement[0m[2m, another[0m[2m order may[0m[2m have already[0m[2m consumed that[0m[2m inventory.[0m[2m The `[0m[2mcheck[0m[2m_stock`[0m[2m method looks[0m[2m safe[0m[2m initially[0m[2m since it[0m[2m just[0m[2m reads values[0m[2m, yet[0m[2m the async[0m[2m delay[0m[2m creates a[0m[2m window where[0m[2m inventory[0m[2m state[0m[2m can[0m[2m shift[0m[2m before[0m[2m any[0m[2m action[0m[2m is taken[0m[2m.[0m[2m
     
     This[0m[2m leads[0m[2m to two[0m[2m distinct[0m[2m failure modes[0m[2m. First[0m[2m, the[0m[2m ghost[0m[2m charge scenario[0m[2m where payment[0m[2m succeeds but[0m[2m inventory can't[0m[2m be decre[0m[2mmented—the[0m[2m current[0m[2m implementation[0m[2m simply[0m[2m logs the[0m[2m error and[0m[2m returns,[0m[2m leaving the[0m[2m customer charged[0m[2m without a[0m[2m product.[0m[2m Second,[0m[2m there's[0m[2m a deeper[0m[2m synchronization[0m[2m issue:[0m[2m nothing[0m[2m prevents[0m[2m the[0m[2m same[0m[2m order[0m[2m_id[0m[2m from being[0m[2m charged multiple[0m[2m times.[0m[2m Although[0m[2m the[0m[2m current[0m[2m test[0m[2m setup[0m[2m appears[0m[2m to[0m[2m generate[0m[2m unique orders[0m[2m, the[0m[2m `[0m[2mcharge[0m[2m` method[0m[2m itself lacks[0m[2m idempot[0m[2mency checks[0m[2m,[0m[2m allowing duplicate[0m[2m transactions[0m[2m for[0m[2m identical[0m[2m order[0m[2m identifiers[0m[2m.[0m[2m 0[0m[2m >=[0m[2m quantity[0m[2m:[0m[2m`,[0m[2m and[0m[2m since quantity[0m[2m is[0m[2m 1,[0m[2m this[0m[2m would[0m[2m pass[0m[2m. So[0m[2m stock[0m[2m could go[0m[2m from[0m[2m 1 to[0m[2m 0[0m[2m, or[0m[2m 2[0m[2m to[0m[2m 1,[0m[2m but[0m[2m never below[0m[2m 0[0m[2m.[0m[2m
     
     I[0m[2m see[0m[2m the guard[0m[2m prevents[0m[2m negative stock[0m[2m, yet[0m[2m it's[0m[2m still possible[0m[2m to overs[0m[2mell.[0m[2m If[0m[2m two[0m[2m orders check[0m[2m stock when[0m[2m only[0m[2m one[0m[2m item remains[0m[2m, both[0m[2m see[0m[2m `[0m[2mself[0m[2m._stock[0m[2m >=[0m[2m quantity[0m[2m` as[0m[2m True[0m[2m.[0m[2m Then[0m[2m both[0m[2m decrement[0m[2m, resulting[0m[2m in stock[0m[2m at[0m[2m -1[0m[2m. The[0m[2m issue[0m[2m is `[0m[2mcheck_stock[0m[2m` creates[0m[2m a window[0m[2m where multiple[0m[2m orders can[0m[2m observe[0m[2m available[0m[2m inventory[0m[2m before any[0m[2m of[0m[2m them actually[0m[2m claim[0m[2m it.[0m[2m Even[0m[2m with[0m[2m the[0m[2m guard in[0m[2m `de[0m[2mcrement`,[0m[2m the check[0m[2m itself[0m[2m isn't[0m[2m atomic with[0m[2m the decrement[0m[2m operation,[0m[2m allowing multiple[0m[2m orders to[0m[2m pass the[0m[2m stock[0m[2m check simultaneously[0m[2m.[0m[2m the[0m[2m same[0m[2m time[0m[2m.[0m[2m Order[0m[2m A charges[0m[2m successfully[0m[2m and[0m[2m decrements[0m[2m stock[0m[2m from[0m[2m 1[0m[2m to[0m[2m 0.[0m[2m But[0m[2m then[0m[2m Order[0m[2m B's[0m[2m charge also[0m[2m succeeds[0m[2m because[0m[2m the[0m[2m gateway[0m[2m has[0m[2m no safeguard[0m[2m against processing[0m[2m the same[0m[2m order twice[0m[2m. Both[0m[2m charges[0m[2m go[0m[2m through,[0m[2m yet[0m[2m only[0m[2m one item[0m[2m existed[0m[2m.[0m[2m
     
     This[0m[2m reveals[0m[2m two[0m[2m critical flaws[0m[2m: the[0m[2m payment[0m[2m gateway allows[0m[2m duplicate charges[0m[2m for identical[0m[2m order IDs[0m[2m without[0m[2m validation[0m[2m, and[0m[2m the checkout[0m[2m flow processes[0m[2m payments[0m[2m before reserving[0m[2m inventory.[0m[2m When[0m[2m stock[0m[2m verification[0m[2m happens[0m[2m independently[0m[2m of payment[0m[2m processing[0m[2m, multiple[0m[2m concurrent[0m[2m requests[0m[2m can slip[0m[2m through the[0m[2m cracks[0m[2m.[0m[2m The real[0m[2m solution[0m[2m requires[0m[2m locking[0m[2m stock[0m[2m before[0m[2m charging[0m[2m, or[0m[2m making[0m[2m the charge[0m[2m operation itself[0m[2m verify[0m[2m availability[0m[2m atom[0m[2mically.[0m[2m 1[0m[2m. The[0m[2m `[0m[2mcharge[0m[2m` method[0m[2m uses[0m[2m a[0m[2m list[0m[2m instead[0m[2m of a[0m[2m dict[0m[2m, so[0m[2m duplicate[0m[2m order[0m[2m_ids[0m[2m are[0m[2m recorded[0m[2m multiple[0m[2m times.[0m[2m 2.[0m[2m Stock[0m[2m can[0m[2m go negative[0m[2m when[0m[2m multiple orders[0m[2m check availability[0m[2m simultaneously—[0m[2mboth see[0m[2m stock[0m[2m >=[0m[2m 1,[0m[2m then[0m[2m both decrement[0m[2m, dropping[0m[2m the count[0m[2m below zero[0m[2m.[0m[2m 3.[0m[2m Ghost[0m[2m charges occur[0m[2m when payment[0m[2m succeeds but[0m[2m inventory has[0m[2m already[0m[2m been depleted[0m[2m by another[0m[2m concurrent[0m[2m order.[0m[2m The Payment[0m[2mGateway lacks[0m[2m idempot[0m[2mency checks[0m[2m, allowing[0m[2m the[0m[2m same order[0m[2m_id to[0m[2m be charged[0m[2m repeatedly[0m[2m. A[0m[2m single[0m[2m asyncio[0m[2m.Lock won't[0m[2m solve[0m[2m this either[0m[2m,[0m[2m since it[0m[2m only[0m[2m protects[0m[2m the[0m[2m checkout[0m[2m cor[0m[2moutine itself[0m[2m during[0m[2m execution[