  I[0m[2m can see[0m[2m the two[0m[2m race conditions[0m[2m causing[0m[2m the[0m[2m reported[0m[2m issues:[0m[2m
     
     1[0m[2m. **[0m[2mOvers[0m[2melling ([0m[2mTOCT[0m[2mOU race[0m[2m)**:[0m[2m Multiple orders[0m[2m check stock[0m[2m simultaneously,[0m[2m all[0m[2m see enough[0m[2m inventory[0m[2m, then[0m[2m all decrement[0m[2m. The[0m[2m `check[0m[2m_stock`[0m[2m and `[0m[2mdecrement[0m[2m` are[0m[2m separate[0m[2m,[0m[2m non-[0m[2matomic operations[0m[2m.
     
